title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Striving to make a friend more at ease might put a strain on your finances and your heart now. Obviously, you dont enjoy seeing a buddy down in the dumps. However, you could compromise your own integrity without even realizing it while confusing Neptune conflicts with the emotional Moon in your 11th House of Goals.
